            "title": "《大手成交》小米一手87萬股非自動對盤,涉資4611萬元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社12日專訊》小米(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01810:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01810\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01810-HK</a>)於3:20pm錄得1手87萬股非自動對盤,每股造53元,較上日收市價低2%,涉資4611萬元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　小米現價跌3.2%,報52.35元;成交1.12億股,成交金額59.18億元,主動買沽比率36:64,資金淨主動賣出16.08億元。(rw)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
